articles.author: Katia Riddle
articles.title: Trump cuts threaten access to birth control for millions of women - NPR
articles.description: Birth control is routine for many Americans and polls show it's popular across party lines. Now, the Trump administration is withholding funds that provide contraception for low income people.
articles.content:
Contraception is a routine part of life for many Americans and polls show people across political parties agree that it should be legal and accessible.
